00:10:41.910 --> 00:10:43.970 align:middle line:90%
than a few minutes without--

00:10:43.970 --> 00:10:46.740 align:middle line:90%
the breath.

00:10:46.740 --> 00:10:50.100 align:middle line:10%
>> The method I like the most
