inducing an altered state

00:11:12.960 --> 00:11:14.760 align:middle line:90%
without medicines--

00:11:14.760 --> 00:11:19.620 align:middle line:84%
like extreme physical exertion,
or an illness, or injury,

00:11:19.620 --> 00:11:20.940 align:middle line:90%
or something like that--

00:11:20.940 --> 00:11:26.350 align:middle line:84%
