00:11:36.650 --> 00:11:38.190 align:middle line:90%
hour and and a half.

00:11:38.190 --> 00:11:42.480 align:middle line:84%
To me, that makes it very
accessible for somebody

00:11:42.480 --> 00:11:44.435 align:middle line:84%
